<section class="feature3" style=" border: 2px solid #B22222; background-color: #FFFDE5;" data-index="1339">
<h4 class="red" data-index="1340"><span class="underlying" data-index="1341">Underlying Concepts</span></h4>
<p data-index="1342">Because bond issue costs do not meet the definition of an asset, some argue they should be expensed at issuance.</p>
</section>
</aside>
