</figcaption>
</figure>
<p data-index="2241"><span epub:type="pagebreak" role="doc-pagebreak" title="14-14" id="Page_14-14" data-index="2242"></span>General Bell records the reacquisition and cancellation of the bonds as follows.</p>
<table style=" width: 50%;" data-index="2243">
<tbody data-index="2244">
