<p id="c14-ex-0061" data-index="6845"><b data-index="6846"><span class="codeColorBlue2" data-index="6847">P14.9</span></b> <span class="red" data-index="6848"><b data-index="6849">(LO <a href="#lo_3" data-index="6850" data-section-index="24" data-section-idref="lo_3" data-target-data-index="2313">3</a>)</b></span> <b data-index="6851">(Entries for Zero-Interest-Bearing Note; Payable in Installments)</b> Sabonis Cosmetics Co. purchased machinery on December 31, 2019, paying $50,000 down and agreeing to pay the balance in four equal installments of $40,000 payable each December 31. An assumed interest of 8% is implicit in the purchase price.</p>
<h4 data-index="6852"><span class="red" data-index="6853">Instructions</span></h4>
