<h4 data-index="7098"><span class="red" data-index="7099">Instructions</span></h4>
<p class="latin1" data-index="7100"><span class="label" data-index="7101"><b data-index="7102">a.</b>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span> Compute the new effective-interest rate for Crocker Corp. following restructure. (<i data-index="7103">Hint:</i> Find the interest rate that establishes approximately $363,000 as the present value of the total future cash flows.)</p>
<p class="latin1" data-index="7104"><span class="label" data-index="7105"><b data-index="7106">b.</b>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span> Prepare a schedule of debt reduction and interest expense for the years 2020 through 2023.</p>
