<p class="latin1" data-index="7110"><span class="label" data-index="7111"><b data-index="7112">d.</b>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span> Prepare all the necessary journal entries on the books of Crocker Corp. for the years 2020, 2021, and 2022.</p>
<p class="latin1" data-index="7113"><span class="label" data-index="7114"><b data-index="7115">e.</b>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span> Prepare all the necessary journal entries on the books of D. Yaeger Corp. for the years 2020, 2021, and 2022.</p>
