<p data-index="8631">Solving algebraically for <i data-index="8632">i</i>, we find that <span data-index="8633"><i data-index="8634">i</i> = 3.46613%</span>.</p></aside>
<aside class="noteEntry" data-index="8635"><p data-index="8636"><a id="c14-note-0020-a" href="#c14-note-0020" data-index="8637" data-section-index="24" data-section-idref="c14-note-0020" data-target-data-index="4874"><sup data-index="8638">20</sup></a> Total interest payments are <span data-index="8639">$7,000,000 × .08 × 4 years = $2,240,000</span>.</p></aside>
